ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the Customs Tariff, 2011-3
PrecisOrder Amending the Schedule to the CUSTOMS TARIFF, 2011-3, in order to eliminate tariffs on certain goods used by Canadian manufacturers in their operations. This is consistent with longstanding tariff policy and the government’s commitment to make Canada a tariff-free zone for industrial manufacturers.
